
'dup word? true == check
'nonexistent word? false == check
"dup" word? false == check

'dup var? false == check
[ | x | 'x var? ] 123 swap exec true == check
'x var? false == check

10 number? true == check
10.5 number? true == check
"hello" number? false == check
inf inf? true == check
nan nan? true == check
10.0 nan? false == check
